dfischer.utils

Class PerformanceDataTickExtension

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.PerformanceDataTickExtension

  • public class PerformanceDataTickExtension
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains additional data about single measured URL calls.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int EXT_TYPE_ALL
      Collect all: the request and the response header - and the request and the response content of URL call and also additional performance details.
      static int EXT_TYPE_ALL_WITHOUT_RESPONSE_CONNTENT
      Collect the request header, the response content and the response header of URL call and also additional performance details.
      static int EXT_TYPE_INDEPTH_PERFORMANCE_DETAILS_PER_URL_CALL
      Collect (only) full performance details of URL call inclusive in-depth throughput data of the HTTP response content - but without the request/response headers and without the content data
      static int EXT_TYPE_NOTYPE
      Invalid initial value - collect nothing.
      static int EXT_TYPE_PERFORMANCE_DETAILS_PER_URL_CALL
      Collect (only) additional performance details of URL call - without the request/response headers and without the content data.
      static int EXT_TYPE_REQUEST_ALL
      Collect the request header and the request content of URL call and also additional performance details.
      static int EXT_TYPE_REQUEST_CONTENT
      Collect the request content of URL call and also additional performance details.
      static int EXT_TYPE_REQUEST_HEADER
      Collect the request header of URL call and also additional performance details.
      static int EXT_TYPE_RESPONSE_ALL
      Collect response header and response content of URL call and also additional performance details.
      static int EXT_TYPE_RESPONSE_HEADER
      Collect the response header of URL call and also additional performance details.
      static int EXT_TYPE_TCPIP_CLIENT_DATA
      Collect TCP/IP client data such as IP client address, IP client port, and SSL ID (for encrypted connections), and also additional performance details.
